                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/19883</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Vera Cruz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-11-15T22:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 15, 1916, 10 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Now learned no American casualties Inter-Oceanic accident except those mentioned
                    my November 14, 6 p.m. Vera Cruz State military commander sends messenger to
                    tell me he will punish severely soldiers for wholesale robbing wounded and
                    killed in wreck.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Canada</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
